title: Sauder North Avenue Cart/Pantry cabinets, L: 32.76" x W: 17.28" x H: 36.02", Charter Oak finish
description: Keep the fun and entertainment rolling through your home with this multi-purpose cart from the North Avenue® collection. This clean-cut rolling cart features two spacious shelves for drinks, glasses, or your favorite appetizer. Entertainment is made easy with the easy-roll casters on this bar cart that allow it to move from room to room so the party is never limited to one space. Constructed with a durable, black metal frame and finished on all surfaces in Charter Oak™, this versatile 2 shelf cart is sure to be a crowd pleaser in any room. We hope you like what you see with this industrial rolling cart. Sauder designers travel the world and bring back the best and latest in style, finish, and color trends. This inspiring world travel is evident in the cutting edge and innovative furniture solutions we offer to you!
